► Onchain activity: tracks your Solana blockchain participation. This includes token swaps, staking SOL, NFT minting, and DeFi interactions;

► dApp exploration: measures how you use apps from the Solana dApp Store;

► Daily use: monitors how you integrate Seeker into your daily routine.

